DataMigrate.Model

Class MigratorMessages

  • java.lang.Object
    • DataMigrate.Model.MigratorMessages

  • public class MigratorMessages
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will contain all of the messages relating to the data migrator's text areas. Most of the messages here will contains steps on how to complete each page of the program. Created by Anthony Orio on 5/2/2017.
